297
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:49,120
They’ve collected evidence

298
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,250
about Pear Blossom.

299
00:16:50,680 --> 00:16:52,080
I’ll call the police and let them

300
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:53,480
investigate Mr. Yang.

301
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:54,400
You guys leave first.

302
00:16:54,400 --> 00:16:55,320
