311
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:04,200
Weixun!

312
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:15,839
Right!

313
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:19,680
They are here for Pear Blossom.

314
00:17:21,760 --> 00:17:22,760
