319
00:17:35,360 --> 00:17:36,120
Don’t worry.

320
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:40,280
I’ll make sure he’s safe.

321
00:17:42,340 --> 00:17:43,880
I’ve locked up those

322
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:45,900
