323
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,100
Don’t worry.

324
00:17:48,680 --> 00:17:49,480
That’s right.

325
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:52,360
Get rid of them?

326
00:17:52,520 --> 00:17:53,000
Well…

327
00:17:54,100 --> 00:17:55,500
