330
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:02,400
Can’t we just scare them off?

331
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:03,570
It’s not necessary.

332
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:05,800
You know

333
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:07,980
