335
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:12,840
Hello?

336
00:18:13,600 --> 00:18:15,860
Some people got kidnapped in Joy Winery.

337
00:18:17,080 --> 00:18:17,680
Who are you?

338
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:18,010
Move!

339
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:18,680
What?

340
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:20,580
What are you doing?

341
00:18:23,080 --> 00:18:23,520
Move!

342
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:32,760
