346
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:40,680
I’m not sure I follow you!

347
00:18:41,040 --> 00:18:42,040
Don’t play dumb!

348
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:43,840
I know

349
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:45,500
