368
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:40,340
Yang!

369
00:19:40,840 --> 00:19:42,120
What’s going on?

370
00:19:43,340 --> 00:19:44,160
Honey?

371
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:45,520
How did you…

372
