00:22:31,680 --> 00:22:33,010
Because of your family,

411
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:36,480
I’m the only one left in mine.

412
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:38,560
When I was little,

413
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:40,560
my parents had me

