419
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:55,000
Until one day, my dad was gone.

420
00:22:56,800 --> 00:22:58,440
And my mom was in deep sorrow.

421
00:23:00,480 --> 00:23:01,880
To get justice for my dad,

422
