00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:21,410
Then my mom tried to find my dad all over the place.

428
00:23:21,840 --> 00:23:23,570
But she fell ill not long after.

429
00:23:24,560 --> 00:23:26,690
Ironically, it was such a small world,

