Wan Zeze.

580
00:32:09,520 --> 00:32:11,120
Will Weixun be in danger?

581
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:13,180
He was so furious just now!

582
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:14,640
It was an emergency.

583
00:32:14,760 --> 00:32:16,290
You need to understand him.

584
00:32:17,360 --> 00:32:18,120
Wan Zeze.

585
00:32:18,280 --> 00:32:20,160
You and your father can’t even tell

586
00:32:20,160 --> 00:32:21,560
who’s good and who’s bad!

587
00:32:21,720 --> 00:32:23,450
Mr. Yang is my father’s friend.

588
00:32:23,760 --> 00:32:25,320
He’s been very nice to me.

589
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:27,760
I don’t think he would do something like that!

590
00:32:27,760 --> 00:32:28,280
No.

591
00:32:28,520 --> 00:32:29,450
I have to go back!

592
00:32:29,560 --> 00:32:30,840
It’s too complicated.

593
00:32:30,960 --> 00:32:32,440
And I brought you guys over there.

594
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:33,480
How could I leave?

595
00:32:33,760 --> 00:32:34,920
I need to go back too!

596
00:32:35,040 --> 00:32:36,160
I can’t leave Weixun alone

597
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:37,890
in a dangerous place like that!

598
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:38,530
Let’s go!

599
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:03,250
Have you gotten rid of them?

600
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:04,440
I have.

601
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:05,960
Don’t worry!

602
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:08,630
If you don’t get rid of them

603
00:34:08,960 --> 00:34:10,120
and the evidence,

604
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:12,120
you will be dead.

605
00:34:13,440 --> 00:34:15,100
Luckily, you are quite smart.

606
00:34:15,630 --> 00:34:16,630
I got it! Got it!

607
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:18,480
Mr. Wan.

608
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:36,880
Hello?

609
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:38,670
Honey!

610
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:40,480
Okay! Okay!

611
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:43,400
I’ll go to pick you up now!

612
00:34:44,040 --> 00:34:45,080
Be patient!

613
00:35:31,640 --> 00:35:32,600
Yi Nanke!

614
00:35:33,800 --> 00:35:34,880
Yi Nanke!

615
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:39,400
Hold on!

616
00:35:40,220 --> 00:35:41,280
How come we are off today?

617
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:41,940
Don’t know!

618
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:43,530
- Why are we off?  - Who cares!

619
00:35:44,700 --> 00:35:45,960
Have you seen Mr. Yang?

620
00:35:46,120 --> 00:35:48,040
- No!  - No! No!

621
00:35:48,160 --> 00:35:49,200
He’s injured!

622
00:35:50,240 --> 00:35:51,170
Look at his hand!

623
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:52,520
Badly injured.

624
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:22,720
He Buzui!

625
00:36:24,080 --> 00:36:25,000
Lu Weixun!

626
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:27,040
I’m here!

627
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:28,440
Hold on!

628
00:36:29,080 --> 00:36:30,120
Mr. Yang said

629
00:36:30,800 --> 00:36:33,800
that he’ll let us disappear together with Pear Blossom.

630
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:34,330
He Buzui!

631
00:36:34,760 --> 00:36:35,700
I’ve called the police!

632
00:36:35,700 --> 00:36:36,600
They’ll be here soon!

633
00:36:36,600 --> 00:36:37,600
Hold on!

634
00:36:40,720 --> 00:36:41,800
Please go!

635
00:36:43,360 --> 00:36:44,640
If he sets here on fire,

636
00:36:45,360 --> 00:36:46,760
it’ll explode.

637
00:36:47,200 --> 00:36:48,720
Then, we’ll…

638
00:36:49,200 --> 00:36:51,200
we’ll all…

639
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:52,640
No!

640
00:36:53,640 --> 00:36:54,360
I won’t go!

641
00:36:55,120 --> 00:36:56,200
I’m right here!

642
00:36:56,680 --> 00:36:57,840
Stop trying!

643
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:59,120
Just go!

644
00:36:59,560 --> 00:37:01,240
You can’t open the door!

645
00:37:01,480 --> 00:37:03,080
I’ll be here with you!

646
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:13,960
I haven’t found your sense of taste back!

647
00:37:17,080 --> 00:37:18,000
Lu Weixun.

648
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:20,760
If

649
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:24,000
I’m gone,

650
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:28,920
will your sense of taste be gone too?

651
00:37:31,520 --> 00:37:33,040
I don’t want my sense of taste!

652
00:37:33,040 --> 00:37:34,160
I only want you!

653
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:36,080
He Buzui! Hold on!

654
00:37:36,220 --> 00:37:37,040
Do you hear me?

655
00:37:44,600 --> 00:37:45,680
Hold on!

656
00:40:05,120 --> 00:40:05,560
Hello?

657
00:40:06,880 --> 00:40:09,080
I want to book two tickets to America.

658
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:12,010
As soon as possible!

659
00:40:24,720 --> 00:40:26,200
The Mr. Yang you talked about

660
00:40:26,200 --> 00:40:27,860
didn’t set the winery on fire.

661
00:40:28,040 --> 00:40:30,320
We found a burnt-out match in the storage house.

662
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:31,520
But we can’t find him.

663
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:32,960
I’ll continue to investigate.

664
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:33,690
Don’t worry.

665
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:35,080
Thanks!

666
00:40:38,480 --> 00:40:41,360
Turns out Mr. Yang still has some conscience.

667
00:40:42,960 --> 00:40:45,400
Because I’m blessed!

668
00:40:46,280 --> 00:40:46,920
See,

669
00:40:47,520 --> 00:40:49,640
shouldn’t you be nice

670
00:40:49,640 --> 00:40:50,970
to a lucky penny like me?

671
00:40:51,520 --> 00:40:52,640
So you mean

672
00:40:53,520 --> 00:40:54,980
I can’t leave you anymore?

673
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:01,040
You injured badly!

674
00:41:02,440 --> 00:41:03,600
Does it hurt?

675
00:41:03,960 --> 00:41:04,600
I’m fine.

676
00:41:04,960 --> 00:41:06,240
Let me see that hand.

677
00:41:06,480 --> 00:41:07,810
It’s not hurt. I’m fine.

678
00:41:08,040 --> 00:41:09,520
Let me see!

679
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:15,480
We’d better get out of here.

680
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:16,480
Come on.

681
00:41:16,880 --> 00:41:17,880
Let’s go see a doctor.

